snippet.title: Wira & Taksa, against the Master of gravity - Trailer
snippet.description: The Master of Gravity is a powerful being who submits the worlds that he finds in his travels through the galaxy. Now it is "Nun's" turn, a peaceful planet, where he has begun to alter gravity and control some of his creatures. That is how the chunky "Wira" and the agile "Taksa", the tho most famous explorers from Nun, must make an epic journey through a world where the gravity has been altered, and also passing various obstacles and traps. Their objetive: Reach the "Master of Gravity"'s ship and defeat him to save Nun.
